text: Jaromír Kudera (born 4 August 1990) is a Czech luger. He competed in the men's doubles event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male lugers Category:Olympic lugers of the Czech Republic Category:Lugers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
